{"tid":1818980,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明反連加特既人諗緊咩","createTime":"2020-01-10T11:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T08:05:14.000Z","uid":47268,"like":18,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0af7754a59bafb9059f736678724530423a90bbc","tid":1818980,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"其實連加特既人生就好似一個冇天賦既平凡人<br />\n用盡佢既努力去跟隨其他天才既步伐<br />\n<br />\n佢冇特別快既速度、又有特別強既技術<br />\n又冇特別廣闊既視野，仲要唔太醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢知道自己先天既不足<br />\n用努力黎彌補<br />\n大家可以見到佢係成隊獌入面最勤力嗰幾個<br />\n跑動量又入，身為攻中又肯番到禁區防守<br />\n唔似前面班大帝唔肯跑<br />\n佢憑住自身既努力先可以喺一隊拎到正選位<br />\n跟本就係一個平凡香港人既寫照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但班反lin一句就抺殺咗佢咁耐以黎既努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7e5a6e3b348aa5159dad1c7e04d6c610bb3822","tid":1818980,"uid":199370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:19:43.000Z","msg":"你會同舊垃圾道歉?"},{"pid":"ad598a1c2bdd97cc6a185bb2a52309de56531d58","tid":1818980,"uid":67144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"71fca702b1a828dea906a9ffd24c2fc62a2482da","tid":1818980,"uid":47268,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ac7e5a6e3b348aa5159dad1c7e04d6c610bb3822","tid":1818980,"uid":199370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:19:43.000Z","msg":"你會同舊垃圾道歉?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"就係你呢啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨係識j入球數助攻數<br />\n<br />\n完全唔識欣賞lin既內在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780270bacdae531f203212fed044c2e9f22d4a9d","tid":1818980,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71fca702b1a828dea906a9ffd24c2fc62a2482da","tid":1818980,"uid":47268,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ac7e5a6e3b348